_:Nbcbe2ee32b574c17a99aa38f802f1a19 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Vicky Beer started her role as Regional Director for North West in September 2022.</p>\n\n<p>Vicky was previously the Regional Schools Commissioner for Lancashire and West Yorkshire. Before her appointment, Vicky was a national leader of education and was the Executive Principal of the West Trafford Learning Partnership, part of the Dean Trust.</p>\n\n<p>Earlier in her career she also:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>was a Chair of the Teaching Schools Council (2011 to 2015) and a peer member supporting the council</li>\n  <li>worked as an Ofsted additional inspector</li>\n  <li>was the Director and founding member of By Schools for Schools, a system-led school improvement body serving the Greater Manchester area</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Vicky Beer was awarded a <abbr title=\"Commander of the Order of the British Empire\">CBE</abbr> in the Queen’s Birthday Honours in 2013.</p>\n\n" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
